title: There's been friction with Canada since 1980s, discussed issue with US: Jaishankar
description: External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar said he expressed concerns over the ongoing diplomatic row with Canada to US NSA Jake Sullivan and Secretary of State Antony Blinken. I think hopefully we both came out better informed, he said. This has been an issue of great friction for many years with Canada, in fact going back to the 1980s, Jaishankar added.
